00:21:18,860 --> 00:21:27,564
And then we would come to a capital improvement plan that says so we have 100 million in deferred maintenance at Medford High School and that may be across 10 different projects.

201
00:21:28,024 --> 00:21:34,207
Here's our capital improvement plan and the specific projects that we're creating, you know, over the next six fiscal years we're going to create

